<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>Red Wing</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>KUIPER/kuiper</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=green&gt;EASY&lt;/color&gt;

Red Wing "Solstice" is a heavy frontline wing, its principle task is to engage opposing capital ships. To facilitate this it deploys 'BB-291 Ascension Of Pride' A heavily reinforced variant of the Altea with perhaps the most elite damage control teams in the whole fleet. The main battery consists of three Type 31B quadruple barrel 308mm autocannon turrets and one Type 31 double barrel 308mm turret. While its hardkill network is substantial the ship lacks soft kill so one must beware of missile strikes. It is also vulnerable to being temporarily incapacitated due to only possessing a single magazine. The ‘Ascension Of Pride' is also supported by a pair of scouting Kyves, though both of them lack any offensive capability of their own and only serve to provide awareness to  The ‘Ascension Of Pride’. It should be noted that while the battleship can take hits, it will last much longer if it uses its upgraded linear thrust to evade as much of the fire it takes as possible.
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder>1</SortOverrideOrder>
